## 关于引用内容的说明 (Notice on Quoted Content)

本仓库的 SKILL.md 与 references/research/ 中包含对豆豆所著小说《遥远的救世主》
（作家出版社 2005 年版）的直接引用。这些引用：

1. 用于学术性的人物思想框架分析与角色扮演 Skill 构建，属合理使用范畴；
2. 每处引用均标注章节出处，且嵌入在原创的分析框架中，非孤立摘录；
3. 原著完整文本与大段连续摘录已通过 .gitignore 排除，不在本仓库分发；
4. 本 Skill 不替代阅读原著——强烈建议使用者购买正版小说支持作者豆豆。

如著作权方认为本仓库的引用方式超出合理使用范畴，请通过 GitHub Issue 联系，
将立即调整或下架相关内容。

The SKILL.md and research files in this repository contain direct quotations
from the novel 《遥远的救世主》(Far Away Savior) by 豆豆 (Doudou),
published by Writers Publishing House in 2005. These quotations:

1. Are used for academic character-thought-framework analysis and role-playing
   Skill construction, falling under fair use;
2. Each citation includes chapter source, embedded in original analytical framework;
3. The complete novel text and large continuous excerpts are excluded via
   .gitignore and are NOT distributed in this repository;
4. This Skill does NOT replace reading the original novel—readers are strongly
   encouraged to purchase the official edition to support author 豆豆.
